# Phase 35: Premium UI/UX Overhaul

This phase focuses on elevating the VibeStream aesthetic from "functional" to "premium/state-of-the-art" by refining micro-details, enhancing depth with glassmorphism, and optimizing layouts.

## Proposed Changes

### [Design System & Globals]
#### [MODIFY] [globals.css](file:///C:/GOLive/app/globals.css)
- [NEW] Introduce refined utility classes for:
    - **Premium Borders**: `.border-premium` (subtle gradient/dual-tone).
    - **Advanced Glass**: `.glass-deep` (higher blur, multi-layered background).
    - **Bento Shadows**: Soft, expansive shadows for depth.
    - **Refined Typography**: Tracking and leading adjustments for "Outfit" font.

### [Core Layout & Components]
#### [MODIFY] [Navbar.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/components/Navbar.tsx)
- Implement a floating glass effect with a subtle "active" glow.
- Refine the search bar with internal depth and a better focus state.
#### [MODIFY] [Sidebar.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/components/Sidebar.tsx)
- Transition to a more "floating" aesthetic with active-item glows.
- Soften the divider lines and improve icon alignment.

### [Core Pages Overhaul]
#### [MODIFY] [Home Feed (page.tsx)](file:///C:/GOLive/app/page.tsx)
- Implement a **Bento Grid** layout for featured content/shorts.
- Enhance `VideoCard` with hover-scale effects and elegant info-overlays.
#### [MODIFY] [Watch Page (WatchClient.tsx)](file:///C:/GOLive/app/watch/[id]/WatchClient.tsx)
- Upgrade the **Halo Engine** for smoother ambient glows.
- Refine the action bar (Hype, Tip, Share) with tonal button designs.
#### [MODIFY] [Creator Studio (DashboardClient.tsx)](file:///C:/GOLive/app/studio/dashboard/DashboardClient.tsx)
- Redesign stats cards into a high-fidelity "Intelligence Bento".
- Improve table legibility with row-hover highlights and refined vertical spacing.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Production build check (`npm run build`) to ensure CSS/Types stability.
- Accessibility audit for contrast and readability in the new "deep glass" styles.

### Manual Verification
- Visual "Vibe Check" across mobile (390px) and desktop (1440px).
- Verify smoothness of all new micro-animations and hover transitions.
